because I was sure

00:08:49.654 --> 00:08:51.114 position:50% align:center
you were from one
of the families!

00:08:51.197 --> 00:08:53.783 position:50% align:center
So there's nothing
special about you at all!

00:08:53.867 --> 00:08:56.911 position:50% align:center
Good luck all
the same, I suppose!

00:08:56.995 --> 00:08:58.621 position:50% align:center
What did she even mean by that?!

00:08:58.705 --> 00:09:00.457 position:50% align:center
That girl is
completely clueless!

00:09:00.540 --> 00:09:03.126 position:50% align:center
If she only knew how
incredible Miyuki is!

00:09:03.209 --> 00:09:07.672 position:50% align:center
Airi Isshiki, huh? She's also
known as Éclair Airi.

00:09:07.756 --> 00:09:09.299 position:50% align:center
A daughter of the
Isshiki family--

00:09:09.382 --> 00:09:11.468 position:50% align:center
one of the 18
assistant houses.

00:09:11.551 --> 00:09:12.886 position:50% align:center
She has a reputation for

00:09:12.969 --> 00:09:15.388 position:50% align:center
piercing Movement Spell
attacks. It's what earned her

00:09:15.472 --> 00:09:18.141 position:50% align:center
that nickname, "Éclair,"
as well as "Lightning."

00:09:18.224 --> 00:09:19.476 position:50% align:center
Oh, wow.

00:09:19.559 --> 00:09:20.935 position:50% align:center
She's only a first year,
but she's competing in the

00:09:21.019 --> 00:09:22.687 position:50% align:center
Official Mirage Bat Event?

00:09:22.771 --> 00:09:25.148 position:50% align:center
That's usually only
for upperclassmen!

00:09:25.231 --> 00:09:28.193 position:50% align:center
The two girls she was with
are also only first years

00:09:28.276 --> 00:09:30.403 position:50% align:center
and both are really impressive.

00:09:30.487 --> 00:09:32.447 position:50% align:center
It's likely that we'll
be facing off with them

00:09:32.530 --> 00:09:34.032 position:50% align:center
in the Rookie Events.

00:09:34.115 --> 00:09:38.370 position:50% align:center
[HONOKA whimpers] Now you've got
me worrying about it, Shizuku!

00:09:38.453 --> 00:09:41.331 position:50% align:center
[knocking]

00:09:41.414 --> 00:09:43.083 position:50% align:center
Hey, Eimi. What's up?

00:09:43.166 --> 00:09:46.628 position:50% align:center
[EIMI giggles] We're heading
over to the hot spring!

00:09:47.712 --> 00:09:50.840 position:50% align:center
[HONOKA sighs]
This feels so nice!

00:09:50.924 --> 00:09:53.760 position:50% align:center
Good find. I wish we
could stay here all day!

00:09:53.843 --> 00:09:55.553 position:50% align:center
[EIMI]
Holy smokes, Honoka.

00:09:55.637 --> 00:09:57.639 position:50% align:center
I had no idea you
were so stacked.

00:09:57.722 --> 00:09:58.890 position:50% align:center
[HONOKA]
Huh?

00:09:58.973 --> 00:10:01.643 position:50% align:center
Ya mind giving me a peek?

00:10:01.726 --> 00:10:03.603 position:50% align:center
Of course I mind, Eimi!

00:10:03.687 --> 00:10:05.939 position:50% align:center
Then I'll just massage them!

00:10:06.022 --> 00:10:08.316 position:50% align:center
