What are you doing?

00:10:08.400 --> 00:10:10.777 position:50% align:center
[HONOKA yelps]

00:10:10.860 --> 00:10:12.278 position:50% align:center
I saw this on an anime once!

00:10:12.362 --> 00:10:15.407 position:50% align:center
If I massage them, that lets
me "see" them with my hands!

00:10:15.490 --> 00:10:17.909 position:50% align:center
You've been watching
too much weird anime!

00:10:17.992 --> 00:10:20.370 position:50% align:center
Please! Save me, Shizuku!

00:10:20.453 --> 00:10:22.831 position:50% align:center
Must be nice getting
so much attention.

00:10:22.914 --> 00:10:25.083 position:50% align:center
At least you have
something to massage...

00:10:25.166 --> 00:10:26.334 position:50% align:center
That sounds like permission!

00:10:26.418 --> 00:10:30.505 position:50% align:center
--[HONOKA yelps]
--[EIMI giggles]

00:10:30.588 --> 00:10:33.091 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI] Hello, everyone!
What's all the fuss about?

00:10:33.174 --> 00:10:35.802 position:50% align:center
[GROUP gasps]

00:10:35.885 --> 00:10:37.554 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI] You should
try to keep it down.

00:10:37.637 --> 00:10:40.890 position:50% align:center
