of the other guests, do we?

00:10:50.567 --> 00:10:53.153 position:50% align:center
[GROUP gasps]

00:10:53.236 --> 00:10:57.282 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI] Uh? Girls?
Are you all... doing okay?

00:10:57.365 --> 00:10:59.284 position:50% align:center
