to participate in

00:20:34.984 --> 00:20:35.985 position:50% align:center
the Official Mirage Bat Event.

00:20:36.069 --> 00:20:37.821 position:50% align:center
She's just like Ms. Isshiki;

00:20:37.904 --> 00:20:40.115 position:50% align:center
a first-year in
the Official Events.

00:20:40.198 --> 00:20:43.326 position:50% align:center
She must be an exceptional
athlete... Masaki?

00:20:43.410 --> 00:20:44.202 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:20:44.285 --> 00:20:45.912 position:50% align:center
Angel...

00:20:45.995 --> 00:20:47.539 position:50% align:center
[KICHIJOJI]
Masaki?

00:20:47.622 --> 00:20:48.998 position:50% align:center
[TOKO]
Isn't that...?

00:20:49.082 --> 00:20:50.625 position:50% align:center
[AIRI] That girl
from the get together.

00:20:50.709 --> 00:20:52.127 position:50% align:center
It is, isn't it?

00:20:52.210 --> 00:20:55.088 position:50% align:center
Well, seems we may
have underestimated her.

00:20:55.171 --> 00:20:57.507 position:50% align:center
Airi, I'm counting on you
to win against that girl,

00:20:57.590 --> 00:20:59.342 position:50% align:center
no matter what.

00:20:59.426 --> 00:21:01.261 position:50% align:center
Okay? And I'm not
just saying that

00:21:01.344 --> 00:21:03.263 position:50% align:center
because she's
Watanabe's replacement.

00:21:03.346 --> 00:21:05.348 position:50% align:center
It's a great opportunity
for you, too,

00:21:05.432 --> 00:21:07.976 position:50% align:center
to make your grand debut.

00:21:08.059 --> 00:21:09.227 position:50% align:center
And for my part,

00:21:09.310 --> 00:21:11.438 position:50% align:center
I'll do everything in my
power to support you.

00:21:11.521 --> 00:21:14.983 position:50% align:center
Because, Airi, you are the
pride of Third High School.

00:21:15.066 --> 00:21:16.860 position:50% align:center
Thank you, Ms. Mizuo...

00:21:18.695 --> 00:21:20.405 position:50% align:center
[AIRI] But I need more
than your support.

00:21:20.488 --> 00:21:24.284 position:50% align:center
I want us to claim this victory
together, hand in hand!

00:21:24.367 --> 00:21:26.453 position:50% align:center
Let's show them what
Third High is capable of

00:21:26.536 --> 00:21:29.956 position:50% align:center
and go for a one-two finish
in the Mirage Bat Event!

00:21:34.878 --> 00:21:35.962 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
They're finally starting

00:21:36.046 --> 00:21:38.715 position:50% align:center
the Rookie Events today!
Let's do our best!

00:21:38.798 --> 00:21:40.175 position:50% align:center
[HONOKA grunts]
Yeah.

00:21:40.258 --> 00:21:41.718 position:50% align:center
How are you doing?

00:21:41.801 --> 00:21:43.928 position:50% align:center
It must be a lot to handle,
taking on Ms. Watanabe's matches

00:21:44.012 --> 00:21:45.930 position:50% align:center
