in the Rookie Events.

00:21:46.014 --> 00:21:47.265 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
You're not wrong...

00:21:47.349 --> 00:21:49.684 position:50% align:center
But I'll be just fine!
I mean, after all,

00:21:49.768 --> 00:21:51.686 position:50% align:center
I have my brother to back me up!

00:21:51.770 --> 00:21:53.355 position:50% align:center
 Right, yeah, of course!

00:21:53.438 --> 00:21:55.190 position:50% align:center
So there's nothing
to fear, Miyuki!

00:21:55.273 --> 00:21:57.525 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI] By the way,
the same goes for you, y'know.

00:21:57.609 --> 00:21:58.943 position:50% align:center
[HONOKA, SHIZUKU]
Huh?

00:21:59.027 --> 00:22:00.862 position:50% align:center
When you've needed help
with your strategy or training,

00:22:00.945 --> 00:22:03.406 position:50% align:center
who's always been there to
lend a hand no matter what?

00:22:03.490 --> 00:22:05.116 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:22:05.200 --> 00:22:07.827 position:50% align:center
Yeah. I guess you're right.

00:22:07.911 --> 00:22:09.454 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI chuckles]

00:22:09.537 --> 00:22:10.705 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
The three of us

00:22:10.789 --> 00:22:13.375 position:50% align:center
are going to give this
everything we've got.

00:22:13.458 --> 00:22:16.086 position:50% align:center
Please watch over us,
Big Brother!